CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FWords by Producer Lois Smith
OL,9,FA woman who is among the more than
OL,10,F1,700 people seeking legal action
OL,11,Fagainst travel company Tui after
OL,12,Fbecoming ill while on holiday in Cape
OL,13,FVerde told ITV News she is "still
OL,14,Fsuffering" from long-term health
OL,15,Fproblems.
OL,17,FNicky Morley, 55, from Devon,
OL,18,Fholidayed at the five-star Riu Palace
OL,19,FSanta Maria in May 2022, with her
OL,20,Fhusband, when she became so ill that
OL,21,Fshe thought she was "going to die".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,F"I was trying to get breath, but (the
OL,8,Fvomiting was) so strong and so
OL,9,Fviolent, I started to choke, and I was
OL,10,Freally panicking," she said.
OL,12,F"It started again but blood started
OL,13,Fcoming up, and I found that my throat
OL,14,Fwas constricting."
OL,16,FAfter extensive appointments, scans,
OL,17,Fand hospitalisation back in the UK,
OL,18,FMiss Morley says she eventually
OL,19,Freceived a shigella diagnosis.
OL,26,@oD@bpmpD@MpntD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FShigella is a bacterial infection that
OL,8,Fcan cause severe diarrhoea and stomach
OL,9,Fcramps, and can be spread through
OL,10,Ffecal-oral transmission.
OL,12,FBut things did not get better, she
OL,13,Fsaid, as in February 2024 she was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with post-infectious bowel
OL,15,Fdisease.
OL,17,FThe disease is still affecting her day-
OL,18,Fto-day life four years later, causing
OL,19,Fher to frequently "vomit for no
OL,20,Freason".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,F"I could eat the blandest food, which
OL,8,Fyou have to, and suddenly you're just
OL,9,Fill for days," she told ITV News.
OL,11,FShe said she is now "permanently in a
OL,12,Fstate of constipation or diarrhea",
OL,13,Frequiring a bowel emergency card due
OL,14,Fto unexpected bowel releases.
OL,16,F"It affects you mentally as well",
OL,17,FMiss Morley added. "I started getting
OL,18,Fanxiety over where we were staying. I
OL,19,Fdon't eat anywhere new."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FMiss Morley said she already suffered
OL,8,Ffrom "very mild IBS" before her
OL,9,Fholiday; however, "this is a whole new
OL,10,Fball game".
OL,12,FLaw firm Irwin Mitchell has launched
OL,13,FHigh Court proceedings on behalf of
OL,14,Fhundreds of affected holidaymakers and
OL,15,Fis investigating more than 1,700 cases
OL,16,Fwhere individuals stayed at hotels and
OL,17,Fresorts in Cape Verde, many of which
OL,18,Fare operated by Tui.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FIn the most serious cases, lawyers say
OL,8,Fthey are investigating fatalities. It
OL,9,Fis thought that a total of eight Brits
OL,10,Fhave died after falling sick on the
OL,11,FAfrican island since 2023.
OL,13,FMiss Morley believes it was
OL,14,Fundercooked pork served at the
OL,15,Fresort's poolside BBQ that made her
OL,16,Fsick.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FIn a statement, RIU Hotels & Resorts
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are unable to provide any
OL,9,Fcomments regarding the health or
OL,10,Fspecific details of our guests' stays
OL,11,Fout of respect to data protection
OL,12,Fregulations.
OL,14,F"However, we wish to reiterate that
OL,15,FRIU Hotels & Resorts operates under
OL,16,Fthe highest standards of safety and
OL,17,Fhygiene; the wellbeing of the more
OL,18,Fthan 1.6 million guests we have
OL,19,Fwelcomed since 2022 to our hotels in
OL,20,FCape Verde remains our absolute
OL,21,Fpriority."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FA UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fwarning for British travellers has
OL,9,Fbeen in place since February, as they
OL,10,Finvestigate an "increase in reports of
OL,11,FShigella sonnei and Salmonella
OL,12,Finfection in travellers returning from
OL,13,FCape Verde".
OL,15,FIrwin Mitchell told ITV News clients
OL,16,Fhave reported "contracting severe
OL,17,Fgastric illnesses, including E. coli,
OL,18,Fsalmonella, shigella, and parasitic
OL,19,Finfections such as cryptosporidium",
OL,20,Fwith many requiring hospital treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FThey add that some claims involve
OL,8,F"longterm health complications and,
OL,9,Fin the most serious circumstances,
OL,10,Ffatalities", and that "it is alleged
OL,11,Fthat the illnesses may be linked to
OL,12,Fpoor hygiene standards and food safety
OL,13,Ffailings".
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
