FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FMiss Morley is not the only person who
OL,8,Fsaid they are still suffering after
OL,9,Ftheir initial sickness.
OL,11,FNicola Witham, aged 43 from Sheffield,
OL,12,Falso holidayed in the Cape Verde
OL,13,Fresort with her family in January this
OL,14,Fyear, and, like Miss Morley, said she
OL,15,Fexperienced a fever, profuse sweating,
OL,16,Fand sickness with lasting effects.
OL,18,FMrs Witham visited the resort from
OL,19,FDecember 27, 2025 ` January 3, 2026,
OL,20,Fand began feeling ill the day before
OL,21,Fleaving
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,F"I've never experienced anything like
OL,8,Fit", she told ITV News. "I've had food
OL,9,Fpoisoning before, and that just didn't
OL,10,Fcompare. I can't explain to you the
OL,11,Fpain in my stomach."
OL,13,FUpon arrival back to the UK, Mrs
OL,14,FWitham says she was bedbound for five
OL,15,Fdays, adding: "I didn't move. I didn't
OL,16,Feat".
OL,18,FHer GP confirmed she had salmonella,
OL,19,Fand after two weeks, Mrs Witham had to
OL,20,Fbe given antibiotics as her
OL,21,Ftemperature and sickness persisted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FMonths on, Mrs Witham said: "I'm still
OL,8,Fsuffering now, my stomach is
OL,9,Fdefinitely not back to normal. Some
OL,10,Ffoods I can't tolerate, I've still got
OL,11,Fno appetite. I only eat once a day."
OL,13,FDespite contacting Tui in January, Mrs
OL,14,FWitham said she has not received a
OL,15,Fresponse.
OL,17,F"It's not about money at all", she
OL,18,Fexplained, adding, "they need to take
OL,19,Faction".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FITV News contacted Tui, who, after
OL,8,Freviewing both cases, said: "We take
OL,9,Fany reports from customers who say
OL,10,Fthey became unwell while on holiday
OL,11,Fvery seriously and understand how
OL,12,Fdifficult that experience can be while
OL,13,Fabroad.
OL,15,F"While we cannot comment on individual
OL,16,Fcases, customer health and safety is
OL,17,Falways our highest priority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776506752
OL,3,CTui holidaymaker suffering from
OL,4,Cstomach problems years after 'scary'
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,F"We have clear procedures in place to
OL,8,Fsupport any customer who becomes
OL,9,Funwell, including access to
OL,10,Fappropriate medical care and
OL,11,Fassistance in resort.
OL,13,F"We continue to follow FCDO advice and
OL,14,Fwork closely with our hotel partners
OL,15,Fand relevant local authorities where
OL,16,Fappropriate."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
